    <div id="status-tab" class="content-tab-panel">
            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: Royal College of Nursing, National Institute for Health and Clinical Excellence (NICE). The management of pressure ulcers in primary and secondary care. A clinical practice guideline. London (UK): Royal College of Nursing; 2005 Sep 22. 245 p. [485 references]</p>
<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria.</p></div></p>
    </div>
